{
  "stem": "15732.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of the first things they did-- pardon me-- were taking whoever young people were-- were not that many-- who were young people to enlisting them in the army.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even my father was a-- was taken to the red army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] but-- they tried to take him to the army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he could weed himself out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was at that time, most probably, already 50 or 51.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But, being a tailor, he made a suit for-- for the one that was in the commission and then the other one, and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he stayed with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He didn't have to go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was the first.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Afterwards, a few months later, I started to go back to school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because I-- I wanted to finish my education.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But that was-- in Russia, there were only 10 years of schooling.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was supposed to finish the 10-- the year 10.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But after half a year, maybe, they closed the schools.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they said, it must be-- the effort for the war must be intensified.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the women were supposed to go and work in the coal-- coal mines in-- they were called, in Russian, Donbass.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This is Donetskij bassejn, that is in the middle of Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, that-- it was another hurdle to be overcome.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Very hard to overcome until, through my father's friend, again, I got a job learning to be a projectionist in a cinema again.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He made it through his-- his acquaintances, you know, one man, one person knows this-- the second one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I started to work as a projectionist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that saved me from having being sent away to Donbass.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were under the Russians-- a year later was the end of the war, on the 8th of May.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
